availability_zone.description: The availability zone where the ODB network is located.

availability_zone_id.description: The AZ ID of the AZ where the ODB network is located.

backup_subnet_cidr.description: The CIDR range of the backup subnet for the ODB network.

client_subnet_cidr.description: The CIDR notation for the network resource.

created_at.description: The date and time when the ODB network was created.

custom_domain_name.description: The name of the custom domain that the network is located.

default_dns_prefix.description: The default DNS prefix for the network resource.

display_name.description: Display name for the network resource.

managed_services.description: The managed services configuration for the ODB network.

oci_dns_forwarding_configs.description: The DNS resolver endpoint in OCI for forwarding DNS queries for the ociPrivateZone domain.

oci_network_anchor_id.description: The unique identifier of the OCI network anchor for the ODB network.

oci_network_anchor_url.description: The URL of the OCI network anchor for the ODB network.

oci_resource_anchor_name.description: The name of the OCI resource anchor for the ODB network.

oci_vcn_id.description: The unique identifier  Oracle Cloud ID (OCID) of the OCI VCN for the ODB network.

oci_vcn_url.description: The URL of the OCI VCN for the ODB network.

peered_cidrs.description: The list of CIDR ranges from the peered VPC that are allowed access to the ODB network. Please refer odb network peering documentation.

percent_progress.description: The amount of progress made on the current operation on the ODB network, expressed as a percentage.

region.description: Region where this resource will be [managed](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/general/latest/gr/rande.html#regional-endpoints). Defaults to the Region set in the [provider configuration](https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs#aws-configuration-reference).

status.description: The status of the network resource.

status_reason.description: Additional information about the current status of the ODB network.
